    "Specifically, ANNs play an important role in an Evolvable IDS (EIDS) by detecting malicious clients.",
    "Moreover, federated learning improves privacy by distributing ANN across multiple devices and by aggregating updates from these devices.",
    "This approach increases the model efficiency and significantly reduces the latency associated with model updates.",
    "Table 4 summarizes the key studies, highlighting the balance between performance and privacy techniques for securing FL through ANN-based anomaly detection.",
    "Saura et al. (2022) presented the CyberSec4Europe project, aimed at improving anomaly detection in the Open Banking use case."
